# Layout Working Area Rules

- Keep the main app sidebar pinned to the far left of the viewport.
- Do not stretch page content edge-to-edge when a shell/sidebar layout is used.
- Define a bounded working area for primary page content (for example `max-w-7xl`) and center it inside the main pane.
- Apply the same content-width pattern across top-level teacher pages for visual consistency.
- Preserve existing project visual tokens and component style language when adjusting layout.
